* The fuzor fembot could hear the two male bots arguing about something, still not quite able to warm herself from either of them.
It annoyed her greatly and having them nearly pulling her arms out of their joints wasn't helping, but she couldn't really respond to let them know that.
All she wanted to do was feed and keep warm, whatever way possable.
Food and warmth, and with both of her beast modes the way they were...it was possable to have both at once.
The tugging continued for a bit more before it finally stopped, but she was being moved by the male bots again.
Well, as long as she wasn't being tugged away from either's warmth then it was fine with her.
As she moved she leaned against Bloodystrike for a second and absorbed a bit of his warmth, that was, until she was pulled towards Reptilica and managed to absorbe a bit of his warmth as well.
Whichever one she was pulled towards she leaned against, the shivers not stopping a bit but building her warmth a little at a time.*
